Package: rowpatternmatcher
Title: Select rows based on pattern
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Radbrt", "zu Hohenzolle", email = "dev_null@cerx.co",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Return rows not based not only on the row itself, but its relationship to previous and following rows. Think of it as regex for dataframes.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
